lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth paced onto the green and marked one of the six balls on or around the putting surface in near-darkness at the Abu Dhabi Championship on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: McIlroy, Fowler in 5-Way Tie for Lead in Abu Dhabi
